        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> One very handy feature of a Beastlord is that they always get the very best pet just by casting the appropriate spell for their level. This spell determines the pets damage, AC, HPS, and level. Other pet classes have to keep summoning to get a top hitting pet and when you have a spectre pet you can easily go through 100pp in periodots just to get a blue pet. To me this a nice perk of this class.</P><P>Dornette<BR>60 necromancer (un-retired)<BR>The Nameless<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
